description: Get the, unofficial, status of the new driver application from the New York TLC.  Data comes from  Data.NY.GOV.  For example  Simply Say,  Alexa, open driver application status for  Five seven two one one one four.  (replace these  seven numbers  with the application number you want to look up).   Up to nine information items will be presented.  Including wether your application is complete or incomplete.  To get terms and conditions  say,  More Help. Thank you.
exampleInteractions: ask driver application status for application Five Seven Two One One One Four
ask driver application status for help
imageAltText: Unofficial TLC New Driver Application Status icon
name: Unofficial TLC New Driver Application Status
shortDescription: Get the status of the new driver application from the New York TLC.
